author: dependabot-preview[bot]
body:
Bumps [Microsoft.ApplicationInsights](https://github.com/Microsoft/ApplicationInsights-dotnet) from 2.9.1 to 2.10.0.
Changelog *Sourced from [Microsoft.ApplicationInsights's changelog](https://github.com/microsoft/ApplicationInsights-dotnet/blob/develop/CHANGELOG.md).* > ## Version 2.10.0 > - [SDKVersion modified to be dotnetc for NetCore. This helps identify the source of code path, as implementations are slightly different for NetCore.](https://github-redirect.dependabot.com/microsoft/ApplicationInsights-dotnet/pull/1125) > - [Fix telemetry timestamp precision on .NET Framework](https://github-redirect.dependabot.com/microsoft/ApplicationInsights-dotnet-server/issues/1175) > - [Fix: catch SecurityException when ApplicationInsights config is read in partial trust](https://github-redirect.dependabot.com/microsoft/ApplicationInsights-dotnet/pull/1119) > > ## Version 2.10.0-beta4 > - [Fix NullReferenceException in DiagnosticsEventListener.OnEventWritten](https://github-redirect.dependabot.com/Microsoft/ApplicationInsights-dotnet/issues/1106) > - [Fix RichPayloadEventSource can get enabled at Verbose level](https://github-redirect.dependabot.com/Microsoft/ApplicationInsights-dotnet/issues/1108) > - [Fix DiagnosticsTelemetryModule can get added more than once](https://github-redirect.dependabot.com/Microsoft/ApplicationInsights-dotnet/issues/1111) > - [Modify default settings for ServerTelemetryChannel to reduce disk usage. MaxTransmissionSenderCapacity is changed from 3 to 10, MaxTransmissionBufferCapacity is changed from 1MB to 5MB](https://github-redirect.dependabot.com/Microsoft/ApplicationInsights-dotnet/pull/1113) > > ## Version 2.10.0-beta3 > - No changes. Bumping version to match WebSDK release. > > ## Version 2.10.0-beta2 > - [Fix Transmission in NETCORE to handle partial success (206) response from backend.](https://github-redirect.dependabot.com/Microsoft/ApplicationInsights-dotnet/issues/1047) > - [Fix data losses in ServerTelemetryChannel.](https://github-redirect.dependabot.com/Microsoft/ApplicationInsights-dotnet/issues/1049) > - [InitialSamplingRate is now correctly applied if set in applicationInsights.config] (https://github-redirect.dependabot.com/Microsoft/ApplicationInsights-dotnet/pull/1048) > - Added new target for NetStandard2.0.

[`dcd64ac`](https://github.com/microsoft/ApplicationInsights-dotnet/commit/dcd64ac7b898c3ff6c1d0338e65ccc76e305a518) Bump version to 2.10 stable ([#1141](https://github-redirect.dependabot.com/Microsoft/ApplicationInsights-dotnet/issues/1141)) - [`58ec738`](https://github.com/microsoft/ApplicationInsights-dotnet/commit/58ec738abfbb96c77c1e01abb3b55d0d2fb2e5f5) Merge pull request [#1138](https://github-redirect.dependabot.com/Microsoft/ApplicationInsights-dotnet/issues/1138) from microsoft/tilee/update_test_nugets - [`8040484`](https://github.com/microsoft/ApplicationInsights-dotnet/commit/8040484803f535668e2ca28cd58e39362c252be1) Fix typos in readme.md ([#1132](https://github-redirect.dependabot.com/Microsoft/ApplicationInsights-dotnet/issues/1132)) - [`80025b5`](https://github.com/microsoft/ApplicationInsights-dotnet/commit/80025b5d79cc52485510d422cfa5a0a8159dac83) Correct telemetry timestamp precision on .NET Framework ([#1126](https://github-redirect.dependabot.com/Microsoft/ApplicationInsights-dotnet/issues/1126)) - [`ca4b1eb`](https://github.com/microsoft/ApplicationInsights-dotnet/commit/ca4b1eb3660e69024384b3623ccc177824568d79) SDKVersion to hint NETCORE, other minor changes ([#1125](https://github-redirect.dependabot.com/Microsoft/ApplicationInsights-dotnet/issues/1125)) -
